  w1=0.031, h1=0.2, w2=0.031, h2=0.2, l=0.228,
  R0=gR0, Qc=gQc, alpha=gAlpha, m=m, W=gW)
AT (0,0,0.8+2.5+gGap) RELATIVE PinkCarter

